{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Toggle"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","title":"transaction(_:)","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"iOS","unavailable":false},{"introducedAt":"10.15","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"macOS","unavailable":false},{"introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false},{"introducedAt":"1.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"visionOS","unavailable":false},{"introducedAt":"6.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"watchOS","unavailable":false}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE11transactionyQryAA11TransactionVzcF::SYNTHESIZED::s:11OpenSwiftUI6ToggleV","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"((","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"}],"modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","remoteSource":{"fileName":"TransactionModifier.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Transaction\/TransactionModifier.swift#L84"}},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Toggle\/transaction(_:)"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transform","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV","text":"Transaction","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"transform","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The transformation to apply to transactions","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within this view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all transactions used within the view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Consider three identical animations controlled by a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"button that executes all three animations simultaneously:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The first animation rotates the “Rotation” "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" view by 360"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"degrees."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The second uses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifier to change the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"“Rotation\\nModified” ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" view animation by a factor of 2.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The third animation uses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"text":" modifier to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"replace the rotation animation affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced”","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","type":"reference"},{"text":" view with a spring animation.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code implements these animations:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State private var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation =","                            view.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation = .interactiveSpring(","                            response: 0.60,","                            dampingFraction: 0.20,","                            blendDuration: 0.25)","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    self.flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier on leaf views such as "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Image","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" rather"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"than container views such as "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HStack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transformation applies to all child views within this view; calling"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" on a container view can lead to unbounded scope of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"execution depending on the depth of the view hierarchy."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/toggle\/transaction(_:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Applies the given transaction mutation function to all animations used"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within the view."}],"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/View":{"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/view","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"View","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"View","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type that represents part of your app’s user interface and provides"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"modifiers that you use to configure views."}],"fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Text":{"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/text","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Text"}],"title":"Text","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Toggle/transaction(_:)":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"((","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV"},{"text":") ->